<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHRISTMAS TREES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In light of concern for global warming and deforestation, perhaps it's time for 
us to take another look at our tradition of cutting down a pine tree, putting 
it in our living rooms for two weeks and then throwing it out. 
</P>
<P>
BILL LAURITZEN, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
