<HEADLINE>
<P>
PALESTINIAN LINKAGE ISSUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We are seeing a substantial number of articles about Israel "giving up land for 
peace" in order to settle with the Arab nations on the Palestinian issue. 
</P>
<P>
It is so interesting that never do these same articles indicate that the Arab 
nations should consider "giving up land for peace." 
</P>
<P>
We see a number of articles on the anniversary of the intifada uprising, 
usually accompanied by the number of Palestinians killed by the Israelis during 
their period. Rarely do we see articles written on the number of Palestinians 
killed by fellow Palestinians because they are moderates and seek an alternate 
settlement with Israel. 
</P>
<P>
HAL FEDER, North Hollywood 
</P>
</TEXT>
