in a photo taken on the night Teak was murdered. ; Photo, MURDER TRIAL STARTS: 
Rodney Darnell Garmanian, above, is on trial in the rape and murder of 
18-year-old Teak Dyer in Pacific Palisades in 1988. She was killed just days 
before her graduation from high school. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
