DISTRICT; MEDICAL CARE -- LOS ANGELES; LOS ANGELES COUNTY DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH 
SERVICES; LOS ANGELES BOARD OF EDUCATION; STUDENTS -- HEALTH; NURSES; DOCTORS; 
