</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
BASEBALL PLAYERS -- WAGES AND SALARIES; WELCH, BOB; BASEBALL PLAYERS -- 
CONTRACTS; OAKLAND A'S (BASEBALL TEAM) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA121890-0071 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 323932 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
