SECESSION; NATIONALISM; ETHNIC GROUPS; USSR -- GOVERNMENT; GOVERNMENT REFORM; 
FOOD SHORTAGES; FOOD DISTRIBUTION; USSR -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS 
</P>
