<SUBJECT>
<P>
CRIMINAL JUSTICE; LAW ENFORCEMENT; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; 
COCAINE; CRIME STATISTICS; SENTENCING 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
