<DOCID> 324051 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 18, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
World Report; Part H; Page 6; Column 1; World Report 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
