FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mark Taper Foundation -- A recent $1-million grant to the Los Angeles Central 
Library was made by the Mark Taper Foundation, as reported in a news article 
that appeared Nov. 27. That article and an editorial that appeared Nov. 30 also 
referred to the grant as a donation from financier and philanthropist Mark 
Taper. Although Taper is the sole contributor to the foundation, it was the 
foundation that provided the grant. 
</P>
</TEXT>
