Mortgage &amp; Realty plan -- An article Dec. 11 about a proposed bankruptcy 
court reorganization plan for Mortgage &amp; Realty Trust incorrectly stated 
that the company's creditors and stockholders had approved the plan. The plan 
is still subject to their approval, although committees for both groups support 
the proposal. 
